129
00:11:17,719 --> 00:11:19,053
Yes. A little.

130
00:11:19,137 --> 00:11:21,306
Sorry. My apologies.

131
00:11:24,851 --> 00:11:25,852
Here.

132
00:11:26,436 --> 00:11:27,437
Sit down.

133
00:11:29,230 --> 00:11:31,441
You're Shin Sol-i, right? I'm Seo Ji-su.

134
00:11:32,567 --> 00:11:33,401
Okay.

135
00:11:33,484 --> 00:11:35,612
I have a lot of questions. Can I ask you?

136
00:11:36,529 --> 00:11:38,573
I won't take no for an answer.

137
00:11:39,532 --> 00:11:40,366
Okay.

138
00:11:41,034 --> 00:11:42,702
How did you and Dr. Cha meet?

139
00:11:45,163 --> 00:11:46,372
Why do you ask?

140
00:11:46,456 --> 00:11:48,958
I was wondering if you know her.

141
00:11:49,042 --> 00:11:51,461
Dr. Cha's long-time girlfriend.

142
00:11:53,004 --> 00:11:54,088
"Girlfriend"?

143
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:58,092
But why do you want to know?

144
00:11:59,469 --> 00:12:01,554
Isn't it funny?

145
00:12:02,764 --> 00:12:03,973
What is?

146
00:12:04,057 --> 00:12:06,809
Who dates such a bore like him?

147
00:12:08,603 --> 00:12:12,941
I don't think he's that boring. Is he?

148
00:12:13,983 --> 00:12:18,321
When he was in the States,
he talked about her a lot.

149
00:12:18,404 --> 00:12:21,574
I think he still loves her very much.

150
00:12:22,951 --> 00:12:24,911
That's why I was curious.

151
00:12:24,994 --> 00:12:26,329
Do you know who she is?

152
00:12:28,665 --> 00:12:29,499
No.

153
00:12:38,508 --> 00:12:39,801
What's all this?

154
00:12:45,306 --> 00:12:47,809
All right. Ta-da.

155
00:12:47,892 --> 00:12:50,603
Bring this to Heon.

156
00:12:51,813 --> 00:12:55,316
He asked the surgeons for extra care
for your dad's surgery.

157
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,151
I was so grateful,

158
00:12:57,235 --> 00:12:59,779
so I woke up early in the morning
to pack this.

159
00:12:59,862 --> 00:13:03,032
And eat this with him
after you deliver it.

160
00:13:03,116 --> 00:13:05,326
I prepared two portions in total.

161
00:13:06,411 --> 00:13:10,039
Mom, it's okay. It's past lunchtime.

162
00:13:10,581 --> 00:13:13,126
Be more empathetic, will you?

163
00:13:13,209 --> 00:13:15,420
Didn't you see how skinny Heon got?

164
00:13:15,503 --> 00:13:18,423
